{"tid":622373,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"係茶記食茶餐，最好唔好叫雪菜肉絲同炸菜肉絲。","createTime":"2018-04-09T05:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T12:08:02.000Z","uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4e21eab6ce23fd80e0692caab4633a264b9b8e04","tid":622373,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"你見過一兜好似雜物箱咁嘅一堆雪菜肉絲同炸菜肉絲，雪完解凍，返熱左又雪返，一復一日，又少人叫，直至你班傻鳩接晒貨，先會整兜新嘅。<br />\n你食果兜野，分分鐘經驗過個星期地獄又折返人間，面果浸霉左，撇左佢又賣過，跟本無人會care你嘅生死。"},{"pid":"7f0edfaca767173ab5a79522ca868c6a3dfac811","tid":622373,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"茶記啲野劣，一定架喇，但劣中之霸，一定係雪菜肉絲同炸菜肉絲！"},{"pid":"5699765631a578d80c659c4a5ba85cf79eaf8de2","tid":622373,"uid":579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"沙嗲牛肉都係咁"},{"pid":"3b5ca2c46e3d1d6b3744008c23e017d8f9c7f7aa","tid":622373,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"沙牛因該消耗得快，所以情況好啲"},{"pid":"fc5e615bb85827a68255a840bac64d643786c9de","tid":622373,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bfacf37effcbc58f30bcc5dff641a44e4ccd06","tid":622373,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:15:11.000Z","msg":"學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e025bfc3c741220edde1a7f1d5b7c1cf46a8fb","tid":622373,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9c204769ee1d677615b158aec6e99b1e59d1e2","tid":622373,"uid":125702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:35:24.000Z","msg":"咁午餐肉呢?<img src=\"/asset